videos.description: Tennessee turns the ball over on a fast break, which leads to an open dunk for Wesley Harris at the other end.
videos.headline: Tennessee's blown fast break leads to West Virginia dunk

videos.description: Tennessee's Jordan Bowden makes a great defensive play to get the steal and finishes it off with a fast-break dunk at the other end.
videos.headline: Bowden gets crowd rocking with fast-break dunk

videos.description: West Virginia's Wesley Harris goes for the loose ball but puts his hand on Tennessee's Grant Williams, which earns him a flagrant foul.
videos.headline: Harris get flagrant for slapping Williams
